items.name: JokeRace
items.description: JokeRace is the contest platform for communities to run, grow, and monetize by deploying a contest on any EVM chain. Contests enable communities to submit and vote on entries… and winners to earn rewards. Use cases include bounties, hackathons, grants, awards ceremonies, “best tweet/meme/essay” competitions, persuasion games, feature requests, governance, elections, amendments, etc.
